  "text": "Other variants of CCA-security for encryption considered before include replayable CCA security [CITATION_1] , constrained CCA security [CITATION_2] , and detectable CCA security [CITATION_3] . Notably, these are all relaxations of CCA security, whereas we consider a strengthening. Another strengthening of CCA security previously considered is plaintext awareness [CITATION_4] 1, [CITATION_5] .",
